rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0003
rows.name:
We should head to Aletta as soon as
possible and regroup with the rest
of the resistance.

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah...
We should probably pick up the pace.

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0005
rows.name:
If Aletta is our destination, then we
can make use of the ferry that
leaves from Lascham Cove.

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0006
rows.name:
So we're just going to go in a regular
old boat? Why don't we take the
Emperor's fancy boat?

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0007
rows.name:
Hikari, I'm certain I told you this
before, but we can't pilot military
vessels into Iira right now...

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0008
rows.name:
...Sounds like an excuse for being
mean, if you ask me.

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0009
rows.name:
If I may, Hikari, the person exhibiting
meanness of spirit right now, is you.

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0010
rows.name:
Haha! Good to see Kagutsuchi make
a new friend.

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0011
rows.name:
Your Majesty... I beg to differ. "Friend"
is hardly the appropriate word...

rows.label: campfev11_340_150_msg0012
rows.name:
For once, I agree with ol' bluebottle
here.
